sentences.sentence: We have noticed a big difference between the forests of Chilga and what we have found so far at Mush.
sentences.translation: 我们注意到了 Chilga 的森林和我们在 Mush 找到的森林的一项巨大差异。

sentences.sentence: What really takes me away from it all are the rocks and fossils exposed by and alongside the Mush River.
sentences.translation: 真正把我从这里带走的是因 Mush 河冲刷而暴露在其两旁的岩石和化石.。
